"Congratulations, Mr.
Sedaris. You are an elf."

02:15.700 --> 02:18.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, you can't not
write and keep a diary?

02:18.833 --> 02:22.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID SEDARIS: Well, it's funny,
because, sometimes, people
would say, oh, that's very

02:22.533 --> 02:25.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
