discipline. It is a compulsion.

02:25.700 --> 02:30.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I should be out doing things,
but I have to write about these
people I saw at dinner the

02:32.700 --> 02:36.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
