05:21.766 --> 05:22.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN:
Twenty-first draft?

05:22.900 --> 05:24.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAVID SEDARIS: Mm-hmm.

05:24.366 --> 05:27.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Is it tinkering
