07:11.733 --> 07:13.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes,
for hours sometimes.

07:13.433 --> 07:15.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
DAVID SEDARIS: And I
don't see any part of
that that's negative.

07:15.533 --> 07:17.166 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

07:17.166 --> 07:21.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
DAVID SEDARIS: It's all
I ever dreamed about
like from age to 6 up.

